name: AdverseClinicalReaction
title: Adverse Clinical Reaction
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: Signs, symptoms and disorders resulting from allergic, intolerant, or other reactions to substances.
This list originally derived from IMHC, KP, and VA and based on frequencies.),(Data Element Scope: FHIM: ReactionObservation.reaction),(Inclusion Criteria: clinical manifestations of adverse reaction to a substance),(Exclusion Criteria: grouping concepts, adverse event kinds that are not reactions (medication errors, healthcare-associated infections, e.g.), concepts not under Finding axis)
